    • Field Detail

      • name

        private String name
        User class representing a user in the system. This class is abstract and should be extended by specific user types. It contains common attributes and methods for all users. This class is part of the BTO application system. It is designed to be extended by specific user types such as Applicant, HDBOfficer, and HDBManager. The class provides a constructor to initialise the common attributes of a user. It also provides getter methods to access the attributes.
        See Also:
        Applicant, HDBOfficer, HDBManager

            String userId,
            String password,
            int age,
            MaritalStatus maritalStatus,
            UserType userType)
        Constructor to initialize the User object with common attributes.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the user.
        userId - The unique identifier for the user.
        password - The password for the user.
        age - The age of the user.
        maritalStatus - The marital status of the user (e.g., "Single", "Married").
        userType - The type of user (e.g., UserType.APPLICANT, UserType.HDB_OFFICER, UserType.HDB_MANAGER).
